  "description": "A striking close-up photograph showcases a black butterfly perched on a light-colored, slightly textured stem. The butterfly's wings are fully spread, displaying intricate patterns and textures. The upper wings feature a row of distinct white spots along the outer edge. The lower wings exhibit a more scalloped or fringed edge, and a subtle iridescent blue sheen is visible in certain lighting. The butterfly\u2019s body is black with delicate antennae. The background is a blurred mix of green foliage and warm-toned stems, creating a soft and natural bokeh. The composition is well-lit, with a focus on the butterfly and its delicate features.",
